<template><div><h3 id="vue-常用传值" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#vue-常用传值"><span>vue 常用传值</span></a></h3>
<h4 id="父传子" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#父传子"><span>父传子</span></a></h4>
